HEADWORD: Postfrontal
<hw>Post*fron"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>frontal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated behind the frontal bone or the frontal region of the
skull; -- applied especially to a bone back of and below the frontal in
many animals.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A postfrontal
bone.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

